    "body": "Problem: CompletionItem.labelDetails is ignored, losing function signatures and module info in the completion menu.\r\n\r\nSolution: Append labelDetails.detail to abbr and use labelDetails.description for menu with fallback to item.detail.\r\n\r\nhttps://microsoft.github.io/language-server-protocol/specifications/lsp/3.17/specification/#completionItemLabelDetails\r\n\r\nCloses #32924\r\n\r\nThis is a client-side capability, not a request method; therefore, there is no need to mention it in the news.  if someone feel it is necessary, I can certainly add it.",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-21T23:07:26Z",
    "comment_data": [
        {
            "_links": {
                "html": {
                    "href": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/38403#discussion_r2969591460"
                },
                "pull_request": {
                    "href": "https://api.github.com/repos/neovim/neovim/pulls/38403"
                },
                "self": {
                    "href": "https://api.github.com/repos/neovim/neovim/pulls/comments/2969591460"
                }
            },
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "```suggestion\n      local abbr = ('%s%s'):format(item.label, vim.tbl_get(item, 'labelDetails', 'detail') or '')\n```",
            "commit_id": "f41b923e2f677b9f92ee679dcc2acf5a36d6f42a",
            "created_at": "2026-03-21T13:31:01Z",
            "diff_hunk": "@@ -441,11 +441,16 @@ function M._lsp_to_complete_items(\n         hl_group = 'DiagnosticDeprecated'\n       end\n       local kind, kind_hlgroup = generate_kind(item)\n+      local abbr = item.label\n+      local label_details = item.labelDetails\n+      if label_details and label_details.detail then\n+        abbr = abbr .. label_details.detail\n+      end",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/38403#discussion_r2969591460",
